lead_paragraph: Rohan Davey threw six touchdown passes to help the Dragons beat the Kansas City Brigade, 50-47, at Nassau Coliseum. Davey was 22 of 35 for 233 yards, and Jason Willis had 6 catches for 59 yards and 4 touchdowns for the Dragons (1-1).
